text: 3 Aug 24 (Sat) 6:50 PM - Ordered white noodle, budget mui fan, prawn paste chicken and hot plate tofu for $30.20. It was quite filling for two pax. Food was average at most. White noodle and mui fan lack wok hey. Chicken is red inside. Hot plate tofu was bland. This place is in the middle of nowhere also... Won't come back again.
